Headlines.Author: Polya Lesova
Headlines.Headline: BEFORE THE BELL: US Stock Futures Fall Ahead Of Jobs Data

PARAGRAPH.#text: By Polya Lesova U.S. stock futures edged lower on Friday after the previous session's rally, as investors retreated to the sidelines ahead of jobs data that may provide more clues about the state of the troubled American labor market.
